  08 Jul 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Handling installation of new Notmuch UI for Vim.

  08 Jul 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Cosmetic changes.

  07 Jul 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Ruby bindings. Fixes bug #475624. Thanks and credits to Franz Fellner
  <alpine.art.de@googlemail.com> and Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> and me,
  too. :-)

  20 Jan 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.15::gentoo.

  20 Jan 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org>
  +files/60notmuch-pick-gentoo.el, notmuch-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.15::gentoo.

  18 Jan 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Require libxml2 flag for app-editors/emacs.

  18 Jan 2013; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.14-r1::gentoo.

  19 May 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.13::gentoo, again.

  16 May 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.13::gentoo.

  10 May 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Enforce build with GMime 2.6.

  10 May 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.12::gentoo.

  20 Mar 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Renamed Python bindings README to README-python, because it used to overwrite
  main Notmuch README file.

  20 Mar 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Depend on GMime 2.6.7 or later.

  20 Mar 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  GMime 2.6 must be at least 2.6.7. Latest HEAD is compatible with Python 3.2.

  02 Mar 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.11.1-r2:gentoo and allowed dev-libs/gmime:2.6
  dependency.

  21 Feb 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Added 'nmbug' USE flag.

  24 Jan 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Dropped autotools-utils. Using EAPI4 defaults. Builds with current HEAD, now.

  25 Nov 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Corrected postinst message.

  24 Nov 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> notmuch-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with net-mail/notmuch-0.10 ebuild in Portage Tree.

*notmuch-9999 (24 Nov 2011)

